            "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You are the target of a melee attack.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You're aware of the attack and aren't @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Flat-Footed]{Flat-Footed}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You use your acrobatic prowess to evade an attack, using momentum to keep yourself moving, if you choose.</p>\n<p>You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to AC against the triggering attack. If the attack misses you, you can @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Step]{Step} after the Strike.</p>\n<p>If you're a master in Acrobatics, you can move 10 feet on this Step instead of 5 feet.</p>"
